author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A great after event stream... obviously dedicated to Zatsudan and Superchat reading (In that ocassion is "Supaachaato Orei Time")

An interesting note about themes on this stream is about New PC, and suddenly I remembered one earlier stream on May... I don't know if was the "Mario Kart 8 Deluxe" or the "Animal Crossing" (Or another of now private videos) when before reading Superchats, but after gameplay stream, Rushia shown a Powerful Laptop with many LED lights in the screen case... I remember something about it, and I saw something about this: if the lights are configurable, would show a butterfly, a dokuro, a fandead or even Rushia's face.
